snippet.title: [STEAM] 100% Achievement Gameplay: 100 hidden cats
snippet.description:
Complete playthrough of 100 hidden cats, a single-level hidden-object game. All achievements are just for finding each cat.



Like and subscribe for more content~
Let me know in the comments what you thought about the game or your personal experience with it! Also, feel free to leave any suggestions on fun games or stuff you'd like to see me achievement hunt on Steam.
